                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00">Fol 1v: Ownership note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol 1v: በሰመ፡”… ዛቲ፡ መጽሀፍ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ከመ፡ ትኵኖሙ፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ለደቂቁ፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol 1v: In the name of the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit. One God. This is book is of Gäbrä Krəstos so that salvation may be for his children.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00">Fol 1v: Genealogy of Gäbrä Krəstos. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol 1vr: መባችያ፡ ወለደ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡አምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ፈሲ፡ ለደስ፡ሂ፡ ወለደ፡ ፫ደቂቁ፡ ገብረ፡ ሥላሴ፡ አርአያ፡ ሰላሴ፡ ወልደ፡ ሙሴ፡ ዘውእቶሙሂ፡ ወለዱ፡ ብዙሃነ፡ ደቂቃነ፡ ዘዓልቦሙ፡ ሁልቍ፡ </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00">Fol 2r: Ownership note including details about local governorship. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol 2r: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘዓቡነ፡ ክቡቡ፡ መስፍነ፡ አጋሜ፡ ልዑል፡ እምልዑላን፡  ዘከማሁ፡ ዘዓርዓየ፡ ሀይሎ፡ እመሣፍንተ፡ ዓጋሜ፡ ከመ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሃያል፡ ዘዓልቦ፡ መስፈርት፡ ወይብል፡ አነ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘተዓዘዙልት፡ አጋንንት፡ ወሠይጣናት፡ ወመንግሥቱ፡ ክብርት፡ እመሣፍ[ን]ት፡ ዘነግሠ፡ ህየንቴሁ፡ አምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ በዘመነ፡ መንግሥታ፡ ዘውዲቱ፡ ወመስፍነ፡ አጋሜ፡ ደገዝማች፡ ደስታ፡ ፮ቀን፡ ሃምሌ፡ </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol 2r: This is the book of ˁabunä Kǝbubu (?), the governor of ˁAgame as he is the highest prince(?) who manifested the power from the governors of ˁAgame as Gäbrä Krəstos, immeasurable powerful,Krəstos, </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 116ra: Conmissioner’s supplication for dying.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 116ra: ኦእግዚኦ፡ አእርፍ፡ ነፍሰ፡ ገብርከ፡ አርአያ፡ሥላሴ፡ዕቀቦ፡ ለገብ[ር]ከ፡ ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 116ra: O Lord, let the soul of your servant ˀArˀyayaSǝllase rest and watch over your servant Gäbrä ˀIyäsus.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 116rb: Ownership note and genealogy of Gäbrä Krəstos.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 116rb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘሹም፡ አጋሜ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወገብሩ፡ አምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ [ወለደ፡] ፈሲለደስ፡ ወፈሲለደስ፡ ወለደ፡ ወልደ፡ ሙሴ፡ ገብረ፡ ሰላሴ፡ አርአያ፡ ሰላሴ፡ ዘዓጽሐፉ፡ ከመ፡ ትኵኖሙ፡ ለደቂቁ፡ መድኀኒት፡ ነፍስ፡ ወስጋ፡ ለዘተአመና፡ ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ኢየሀርር፡ ለአለም፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 116rb: This is the book of šum ˀagame Gäbrä Krəstos. And his servant ˀAmdä Mikaˀel [begat] Fäsilädäs. And Fäsilädäs begat Wäldä Muse, Gäbrä Sǝllase, ˀArˀyaya Sǝllase who commissioned the book so that salvation of the soul and the flesh may be for his children [and] for the one who entrusted himself to this book. </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The scribe wrote right beneath the upper ruled lines (i.e. the letters are not set on the ruled line).&#xD;
- The scribe sometimes ignored the ruling and wrote two text lines within two ruled lines (compressed script), e.g., on fols. 8r-15v. &#xD;
- Omitted letters and words are inserted interlineally: e.g., fols. 8ra, 10ra, 18ra, 21vb, 28vb, 31rb, 45va, 49ra, 60rb, 61rb, 79ra, 88ra, 106vb, 111vb, 114rb, 122rb.&#xD;
- Immediate correction is indicated by thin lines above and below the word to be cancelled (dittographic errors):  fols. 10vb, 13va, 22vb, 51vb, 86ra. &#xD;
- Pen trial on fol. 2r.  &#xD;
- Scribbles, crude minor notes: fol. 2v, 21r, 128r.</item>
                     </list>
